---
title: Cheesy Corn Fritters & Kumara Fries with Crumbly Cheese, Turnip Salad & Herby Mayo
description: These gloriously bright fritters are both crunchy and sweet and are set off perfectly by an A-team of dill-parsley mayo, golden
kumara fries and a crunchy turnip salad. If you fancy it, sprinkle some toasted almonds over the salad for ultimate crunch!
